LoggedOut --> AccountCreated : Create Account
AccountCreated --> LoggedIn : Log In
LoggedIn --> ApplicationProcessed : Apply For Visa, Make Payment, Accept Application
ApplicationProcessed --> ViewedStatus : View Status
ViewedStatus --> ViewedStatus : Check Status
ViewedStatus --> FeedbackGiven : Give Feedback
FeedbackGiven --> DetailsModified : Modify Details
DetailsModified --> DetailsViewed : View Details
DetailsViewed --> FinalState : Log Out
LoggedIn --> ApplicationProcessed : Cancel Application
LoggedIn --> DetailsModified : Modify Details
LoggedIn --> DetailsViewed : View Details

